            "title": "《異動股》英諾賽科曾升近三成破20天線兼破頂,現報65.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社20日專訊》英諾賽科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02577-HK</a>)升24.5%,報65.5元,升穿20天線(54.615元),最高價67.6元,創上市新高,最低價53.95元;成交325.59萬股,成交金額1.93億元;主動買沽比率54:46,資金淨主動買入1494萬元。現時最大淨被動買入券商為中國投資信息,金額1475萬元,加權平均成交價59.146元;現時最大淨被動賣出券商為勝利證券,金額499.51萬元,加權平均成交價56.23元。以現價計,該股暫連升4日,累計升幅37.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>65.500</td><td>變動</td><td>+24.52%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>67.600</td><td>最低價</td><td>53.950</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>325.59萬股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>1.93億</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>52.310</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>87.838</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>54.615</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>59.251</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>47.149</td><td>RSI14</td><td>69.167</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">股份狀態:升穿20天線,創上市新高;主動買沽比率54:46,資金淨主動買入1494萬元;暫連升4日,累計升幅37.3%</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>英諾賽科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02577:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02577\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02577-HK</a>)</td><td>65.50</td><td>+24.52</td></tr><tr><td>硬蛋創新(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00400:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00400\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00400-HK</a>)</td><td>1.44</td><td>-2.70</td></tr><tr><td>ASMPT(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00522-HK</a>)</td><td>60.90</td><td>+1.50</td></tr><tr><td>中芯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00981:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00981\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00981-HK</a>)</td><td>51.80</td><td>+1.47</td></tr><tr><td>華虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01347:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01347\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01347-HK</a>)</td><td>37.45</td><td>-1.19</td></tr><tr><td>上海復旦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01385:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01385-HK</a>)</td><td>28.20</td><td>+0.36</td></tr><tr><td>貝克微(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02149:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02149\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02149-HK</a>)</td><td>32.75</td><td>-0.76</td></tr><tr><td>晶門(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02878:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02878-HK</a>)</td><td>0.53</td><td>-1.85</td></tr><tr><td>宏光半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06908:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06908\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06908-HK</a>)</td><td>0.61</td><td>-1.61</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
